item.title: Need help in PimpScape
item.dc:creator: @The_Mentor The Mentor
item.description:
@The_Mentor wrote:

Seriously, don’t post if you don’t have anything helpful to say.

  1. Search for public void MainHelpMenu() and you should see something like this

[code]public void MainHelpMenu()
{
if(playerRights < 4){

				sendQuest("@dre@Main Menu", 8144);  //Title
				clearQuestInterface();
				sendQuest("@dbl@-----------------", 8145);
				sendQuest("@dbl@@dre@~~~@dbl@", 8147);
                sendQuest("@dbl@@dre@ --------------------------", 8148);
				sendQuest("@dre@You last logged in from @blu@"+IPPart1+"."+IPPart2+"."+IPPart3+"."+IPPart4+" @gre@ "+GetLastLogin(lastlogintime)+" @dre@ days ago.@dbl@", 8149);
				sendQuest("@dre@Players online: @gre@"+PlayerHandler.getPlayerCount(), 8150);
                                    sendQuest("@blu@===Your pk stats===", 8151);
                                    sendQuest("@red@Total Kills - "+killcount, 8152);
                                    sendQuest("@red@Pk Points - "+pkpoints, 8153);
                                    sendQuest("@red@Death Count - "+deathcount, 8154);
				sendQuestSomething(8143);
				showInterface(8134);
				flushOutStream();
                               }

else if(playerRights == 1){

	       	sendQuest("@dre@Moderator Help Panel", 8144);  //Title
				clearQuestInterface();
				sendQuest("@dbl@-------------------------", 8145);
				sendQuest("@dbl@@dre@~~~@dbl@", 8147);
				sendQuest("@dre@You last logged in from @blu@"+IPPart1+"."+IPPart2+"."+IPPart3+"."+IPPart4+" @gre@ "+GetLastLogin(lastlogintime)+" @dre@ days ago.@dbl@", 8149);
				sendQuest("@dbl@ -------------", 8150);
				sendQuest("@blu@--------------", 8151);
			        sendQuest("@blu@-----------------------", 8152);
			        sendQuest("@red@ ------------------------------", 8152);
				sendQuestSomething(8143);
				showInterface(8134);
				flushOutStream();
                               }

else if(playerRights >= 2){

				sendQuest("@dre@Admin Help Panel", 8144);  //Title
				clearQuestInterface();
				sendQuest("@dbl@------------------------", 8145);
				sendQuest("@dbl@@dre@------------------------------------@dbl@", 8147);
				sendQuest("@dre@You last logged in from @blu@"+IPPart1+"."+IPPart2+"."+IPPart3+"."+IPPart4+" @gre@ "+GetLastLogin(lastlogintime)+" @dre@ days ago.@dbl@", 8149);
				sendQuest("@dbl@ -------------------", 8150);
				sendQuest("@blu@--------------", 8151);
			        sendQuest("@blu@----------------------", 8152);
				sendQuest("@blu@-----------------------", 8153);
				sendQuest("@blu@-------------------", 8154);
			        sendQuest("@blu@-------------------------------", 8155);
			        sendQuest("@red@ ---------------------------", 8156);
				sendQuestSomething(8143);
				showInterface(8134);
				flushOutStream();
                               }
	
			}[/code]Put whatever you want to the places where is --------'s. And as you can see Main Menu, Moderator Help Panel and Admin Help Panel, whatever you put under the spots where it says for example Admin Help Panel, only the admins see it. If you put it to Main Menu, every player who isn't a mod/admin will see it.
  1. There’s a tut in the tutorial list, called “Making pk zones” if memory serves me well.
